Package io.sphere.sdk.types

Provides model classes and builders for types.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Custom
    Interface to mark objects which can have custom fields, it has nothing to do with CustomObjects.
    CustomDraft
    Interface for draft objects which include custom fields.
    CustomFields
    Custom fields for object extending Custom.
    CustomFieldsDraft
    Draft for CustomFields.
    FieldDefinition  
    FieldType  
    Type
    Types define custom fields that are used to enhance resources as you need.
    TypeDraft
